;NOTE THAT HART CONSTANTS HAVE BEEN SCALED BY A POWER OF 2
;THIS IS DUE TO RANGE REDUCTION AS A % OF 2*PI RATHER THAN PI/2
;WOULD NEED TO MULTIPLY ARGUMENT BY 4 BUT INSTEAD WE FACTOR THIS
